  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 75-29-951, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REMOVE THE CAP ON THE ANNUAL GROSS SALES ALLOWED; TO AUTHORIZE SALES TO BE MADE ONLINE BY MAIL ORDER, AT WHOLESALE, THIRD-PARTY RETAIL ESTABLISHMENTS OR THROUGH AN AGENT OF THE PRODUCER OF THE COTTAGE FOOTAGE, WHICH ARE DELIVERED DIRECTLY TO CONSUMERS IN THE STATE; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
